{"tid":1758414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[英領和你Camp 第十六日］手足們有時間去探下佢地 俾D支持佢地呀","createTime":"2019-11-27T04:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T05:56:58.000Z","uid":22556,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3067ccecf789f8c51cb3dbd0267081f455be5e","tid":1758414,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/27/125417_f3913d43d0b36b42c58dc8ddafeedc7d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F27%2F125417_f3913d43d0b36b42c58dc8ddafeedc7d.jpeg&h=44a177bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🙇🏻&zwj;♀可以幫忙傳出去嗎？🙇🏻&zwj;♀好似無咩人知 和你CAMP活動<br />\n我哋有手足由11月12號起係英領搭營 已經留守咗超過2個禮拜 但愈嚟愈少人嚟英領幫手🤧<br />\n英領有手足精神已經出現咗問題😭<br />\n晚晚d popo都想搞9係英領嘅手足 係灰磚到行嚟行去<br />\n天氣咁涷都仲過夜，又無乜人探佢地，又無乜人同佢地過夜🤦🏻&zwj;♂<br />\n和理非可以幫忙探下英領手足嗎？🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♀<br />\n英領係行英國法律，黑警唔敢搞我哋，但日日都玩小動作，低消為揸狗車上嚟影人頭，壓力好大<br />\n<br />\n各位可因應自身情況調節時間<br />\n早、午、晚、全日均可過嚟<br />\n希望大家可以探下手足🙇🏼&zwj;♀<br />\n嚟唱歌 傾偈 食野 都無問題<br />\n無壓力地和你Camp🤗"},{"pid":"f19ed32dcb29807917bdcc64e58430effd158b00","tid":1758414,"uid":1477,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"哇屌 幾時有咁嘅事 點解無人講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2ff583619a3eeb84ba3c6b61e4dccf8fd14ce1","tid":1758414,"uid":170426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"真係完全唔知<br />\n推俾多啲人知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2549129cfaf16a3e02148c21e6075b9b76231a","tid":1758414,"uid":21234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:09:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b80c602659fd9def063572d83baf567a7c5d794